KarpMmc< GR, CM, TR >::SetPath< T > Struct Template Reference

Detailed Description

template<typename GR, typename CM, typename TR>
template<typename T>
struct lemon::KarpMmc< GR, CM, TR >::SetPath< T >

Named parameter for setting the Path type of the found cycles. It must conform to the Path concept and it must have an addFront() function.

#include <lemon/karp_mmc.h>
